            <title>1.0.2</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 25 Jun 2025 18:47:43 +0200</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>1.0.2</sparkle:version>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <p align="center">
                  <img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3d63fb0d-d961-47ea-bcdd-81394bdc70f4" alt="AeroBrowser Logo" width="250"/>
                </p>

                <h2>v1.0.2 Release</h2>

                <h3>What’s New</h3>

                - 🎨 Redesigned About Page: A more refined layout with improved spacing and clean visuals.
                - 🗒️ New “What’s New” Page: Easily view changelogs and version highlights inside the app.
                - 🌈 Theme Page Overhaul: You can now browse and select themes using a better dropdown picker.

                <h3>Fixes</h3>

                - 🔧 Real Sparkle Fix: Auto-updates are now more reliable.
                - 🐞 Minor bug fixes across UI, including layout glitches and logic inconsistencies.

                <h3>Notes</h3>

                - This release builds on v1.0.1 and v1.0.0 which introduced:
                  - ✅ Ad-blocking
                  - 📚 Bookmarks
                  - 🧠 Search history
                  - 🧹 Reset options
                  - 🔍 Custom search engines
                  - ⚡ Sparkle updater
                  - ✨ New polished UI
                - v1.0.2 improves internal consistency and user polish across the whole experience.

                Bugs? Glitches? Please report them on the [GitHub Issues tab](https://github.com/aerobrowser/aerobrowser/issues)!

                <h3>Logo</h3>

                <p align="center">
                  <img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3d63fb0d-d961-47ea-bcdd-81394bdc70f4" alt="AeroBrowser Logo" width="250"/>
                </p>

