        <item>
            <title>1.0.1</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 24 Jun 2025 23:03:55 +0200</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>1.0.1</sparkle:version>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <p align="center">
                  <img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3d63fb0d-d961-47ea-bcdd-81394bdc70f4" alt="AeroBrowser Logo" width="250"/>
                </p>

                <h2>v1.0.1 Release</h2>

                <h3>What’s New</h3>

                This is a follow-up to the big 1.0.0 release, bringing stability, polish, and new improvements:

                - 🧼 UI Redesign: The homepage and About window now use a cleaner, tighter layout with improved spacing and card presentation.
                - 🧭 About window opens in a native-styled floating window (not closing the whole app anymore).
                - 🔄 Sparkle auto-update integration was fixed — the app now checks and installs updates properly.
                - 🧠 Improved sidebar toggle behavior.
                - 📂 Minor fixes to tab management and memory use.
                - ⚙️ Updated icon spacing and font rendering on smaller displays.

                <h3>Notes</h3>

                - This version builds upon v1.0.0, which introduced ad-blocking, bookmarks, search history, reset options, and more.
                - 1.0.1 focuses on polish and bug fixes from early feedback.
                - Bugs or crashes? Please create an issue in the [GitHub repo](https://github.com/aerobrowser/aerobrowser/issues) so we can squash them 🐞

                <h3>Logo</h3>

                <p align="center">
                  <img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3d63fb0d-d961-47ea-bcdd-81394bdc70f4" alt="AeroBrowser Logo" width="250"/>
                </p>

